headline: 2 Bank Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 That Underwhelm
summary: Banks play a critical role in the financial system, providing everything from commercial loans to wealth management and payment processing services. Furthermore, economic conditions have supported loan growth and fee income, a trend that has enabled the banking industry to return 15.5% over the past six months, almost identical to the S&P 500.
